  Sam-ju7-keng u7 chit8 ku3, kong2, “Jin5 chi chhou, seng3 pun2 sian7.” Koh ti7 pat8 pun2 chheh, kong2, “Jin5 chi chhou, seng3 pun2 ok.” Chit nng7 ku3, long2 piN5-piN5 si7 lan2 Han3-bin5-chok8 ui2-tai7 e5 hak8-chia2 sou2 chu2-tiuN e5, sui-bong2 hit e5 cheng-chha si7 chit8 ji7 na7-tiaN7, iau2-ku2 hit e5 saN-li7 si7 “Liong2 kek8-toan” e5 hng7. Lang5 e5 khi2-goan5 si7 “Ho2” kap lang5 e5 khi2-thau5 si7 “PhaiN2,” chit nng7 khoan2 kek8-toan e5 chu2-tiuN, put-chi2 u7 thang hou7 lan2 chim-chiok e5 sou2-chai7, ia7 put-chi2 tat8-tit lan2 chu3-i3, khak-sit8 lan2 bo5 chu3-i3, ia7 si7 boe7-eng7-tit. In-ui7 chit nng7 e5 chu2-tiuN, si7 choat8-tui3 boe7-thang saN-oa2. Chong2-si7 ki5-sit8 lan2 na7 chim-chiok gian2-kiu3 e5 si5, chit nng7 e5 chu2-tiuN, to long2 u7 i e5 chin-li2 ti7-teh. 
