  Siang5-si5 lan2 tui3 “Seng3 pun2 ok” e5 hong-bin7, ia7 tioh8 kiam2-tho2. In-ui7 khoaN3 se3-kai3 jin5-lui7 e5 lek8-su2, lang5 e5 phin2-seng3 na2-lai5 na2-bai2, na2-lai5 na2 hu2-pai7; to7-tek jit8-jit8 na2 tui7-loh8, ko3-jin5 tui3 ko3-jin5 e5 kam2-cheng5 na2 bai2; ka-teng5 tui3 ka-teng5 e5 chiap-chhiok, na2 sou-oan2; kok-ka tui3 kok-ka e5 koan-he7, na2 li7-khui; bin5-chok8 tui3 bin5-chok8 e5 khi3-hun, na2 pian3 na2 hiong; tai7-ke saN chhai-gi5, khio2-kak8, heng5-hiong, cheng-tou3, bo5 beh saN niu7, ia7 bo5 beh saN sia3-bian2. 
  Tui3 an2-ni, hou7 lan2 kam2-kak-tioh8 u7-iaN2 “Jin5 chi chhou, seng3 pun2 ok.” Ti7 Chhong3-se3-ki2 2:17, 3:1-24, koan-he7 Siong7-te3 sou2 chhong3-cho7, thau5 chit8-tui3 e5 ang-bou2 e5 cheng5-heng5 chin siong5-se3. Chiu7-si7 Siong7-te3 chhong3-cho7 lang5 e5 si5, seng3 si7 “Ho2,” chong2-si7 ui7-tioh8 ui5-keh8, gek8-beng7, bo5 thiaN-than3 chhong3-cho7-chia2 Siong7-te3 e5 beng7-leng7, ti3-kau3 siang5 chit8 e5 lang5, ti7 te2-te2 e5 ki5-kan-tiong tui3 “Ho2,” pian3 choe3 “PhaiN2,” choe3-chhut jin5-lui7 liong2 kek8-toan e5 seng-oah8 e5 khi2-goan5. 
